 succeeded in 0ms:
   241	  `04-task-protocol`. Full state machine enumerated with legal/illegal
   242	  transitions. Exit: state machine is testable (next phase will).
   243	- **Phase 3 — Reference contracts package.** `reference/packages/eden-contracts/`
