   253	- **Phase 6 — Reference storage backend.** `eden-storage` with one
   254	  concrete impl (SQLite for dev). Loop persists.
   255	- **Phase 7 — Reference git integrator.** `eden-git`, `work/*` →
   256	  squash → `trial/*` with eval manifest against a local bare repo.
   257	- **Phase 8 — Cross-process reference: orchestrator + workers over
   258	  a documented transport.** Extract what was in-proc to a wire
   259	  protocol. First point at which a third-party worker in any
   260	  language could participate.
   261	- **Phase 9 — Reference Web UI.** Claim/submit flows for all roles.
   262	- **Phase 10 — Reference Compose stack.** All services in Docker
